---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Why Ionyx? - Ultra-Minimalist Desktop Framework">
	<section class="py-20">
		<div class="container mx-auto px-6">
			<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
				<div class="text-center mb-16">
					<h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
						Why <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-ionyx-neon-purple to-ionyx-neon-blue bg-clip-text text-transparent">Ionyx</span>?
					</h1>
					<p class="text-xl text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
						Masaüstü uygulama geliştirmeyi yeniden tanımlıyoruz. 
						Sadece gerekli olan, fazlasız.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="space-y-12">
					<!-- Agnostic Frontend -->
					<div class="glass-dark p-8 rounded-xl">
						<div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
							<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-r from-ionyx-neon-purple to-ionyx-neon-blue rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
								<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
									<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 20l4-16m4 4l4 4-4 4M6 16l-4-4 4-4"></path>
								</svg>
							</div>
							<div>
								<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Agnostic Frontend</h2>
								<p class="text-gray-300 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
									İstediğin frontend framework'ünü kullan. React, Vue, Svelte, Angular, vanilla JavaScript... 
									Biz senin seçimlerine saygı duyuyoruz. Ionyx sadece backend'i halleder, frontend özgürlüğünü sana bırakır.
								</p>
								<div class="bg-dark-tertiary rounded-lg p-4 border border-dark-border">
									<p class="text-sm text-gray-400 font-mono">
										// Herhangi bir frontend framework ile çalışır<br>
										// Sadece HTML/CSS/JS bilgisi yeterli
									</p>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>

					<!-- The 1.5MB CLI -->
					<div class="glass-dark p-8 rounded-xl">
						<div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
							<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-r from-ionyx-neon-purple to-ionyx-neon-blue rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
								<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
									<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
								</svg>
							</div>
							<div>
								<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">The 1.5MB CLI</h2>
								<p class="text-gray-300 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
									1.66MB'lık CLI'miz inanılmaz bir mühendislik başarısı. 0.44 WRY ve 0.28 TAO üzerine kurulu 
									bu minimalist yapı, hiçbir gereksiz kod taşımaz. Sadece saf performans ve hız.
								</p>
								<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
									<div class="bg-dark-tertiary rounded-lg p-4 border border-dark-border">
										<p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mb-2">WRY</p>
										<p class="text-xs text-gray-500">0.44MB - WebView wrapper</p>
									</div>
									<div class="bg-dark-tertiary rounded-lg p-4 border border-dark-border">
										<p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mb-2">TAO</p>
										<p class="text-xs text-gray-500">0.28MB - Window management</p>
									</div>
									<div class="bg-dark-tertiary rounded-lg p-4 border border-dark-border">
										<p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mb-2">Ionyx Core</p>
										<p class="text-xs text-gray-500">0.94MB - Framework logic</p>
									</div>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>

					<!-- No Extra Runtime -->
					<div class="glass-dark p-8 rounded-xl">
						<div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
							<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-r from-ionyx-neon-purple to-ionyx-neon-blue rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
								<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
									<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 14l-7 7m0 0l-7-7m7 7V3"></path>
								</svg>
							</div>
							<div>
								<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">No Extra Runtime</h2>
								<p class="text-gray-300 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
									Electrobun gibi ekstra bir runtime (Bun) veya Electron gibi devasa bir Chromium 
									paketi taşıma. Ionyx, sistemin mevcut WebView'ını kullanır. Bu ne anlama geliyor?
								</p>
								<ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-300">
									<li class="flex items-start">
										<span class="text-green-400 mr-2">✓</span>
										<span>Windows'ta Edge WebView2 kullanır</span>
									</li>
									<li class="flex items-start">
										<span class="text-green-400 mr-2">✓</span>
										<span>macOS'ta WKWebView kullanır</span>
									</li>
									<li class="flex items-start">
										<span class="text-green-400 mr-2">✓</span>
										<span>Linux'ta WebKitGTK kullanır</span>
									</li>
									<li class="flex items-start">
										<span class="text-green-400 mr-2">✓</span>
										<span>Hiçbir ek runtime yükü yok</span>
									</li>
								</ul>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>

					<!-- Performance Comparison -->
					<div class="glass-dark p-8 rounded-xl">
						<div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
							<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-r from-ionyx-neon-purple to-ionyx-neon-blue rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
								<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
									<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z"></path>
								</svg>
							</div>
							<div>
								<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Gerçek Performans</h2>
								<p class="text-gray-300 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
									Rakamlar yalan söylemez. Ionyx'in performansı diğer framework'lerin gölgesinde kalır:
								</p>
								<div class="overflow-x-auto">
									<table class="w-full">
										<thead>
											<tr class="border-b border-white/10">
												<th class="text-left p-3 text-gray-300">Metrik</th>
												<th class="text-center p-3 text-red-400">Electron</th>
												<th class="text-center p-3 text-yellow-400">Electrobun</th>
												<th class="text-center p-3 text-green-400">Ionyx</th>
											</tr>
										</thead>
										<tbody>
											<tr class="border-b border-white/5">
												<td class="p-3 text-gray-300">Startup</td>
												<td class="p-3 text-center text-red-400">2-5s</td>
												<td class="p-3 text-center text-yellow-400">&lt;50ms</td>
												<td class="p-3 text-center text-green-400 font-bold">&lt;30ms</td>
											</tr>
											<tr class="border-b border-white/5">
												<td class="p-3 text-gray-300">Memory</td>
												<td class="p-3 text-center text-red-400">100-200MB</td>
												<td class="p-3 text-center text-yellow-400">30-50MB</td>
												<td class="p-3 text-center text-green-400 font-bold">10-20MB</td>
											</tr>
											<tr>
												<td class="p-3 text-gray-300">CPU Usage</td>
												<td class="p-3 text-center text-red-400">High</td>
												<td class="p-3 text-center text-yellow-400">Medium</td>
												<td class="p-3 text-center text-green-400 font-bold">Minimal</td>
											</tr>
										</tbody>
									</table>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>

					<!-- Developer Experience -->
					<div class="glass-dark p-8 rounded-xl">
						<div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
							<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-r from-ionyx-neon-purple to-ionyx-neon-blue rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
								<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
									<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10.325 4.317c.426-1.756 2.924-1.756 3.35 0a1.724 1.724 0 002.573 1.066c1.543-.94 3.31.826 2.37 2.37a1.724 1.724 0 001.065 2.572c1.756.426 1.756 2.924 0 3.35a1.724 1.724 0 00-1.066 2.573c.94 1.543-.826 3.31-2.37 2.37a1.724 1.724 0 00-2.572 1.065c-.426 1.756-2.924 1.756-3.35 0a1.724 1.724 0 00-2.573-1.066c-1.543.94-3.31-.826-2.37-2.37a1.724 1.724 0 00-1.065-2.572c-1.756-.426-1.756-2.924 0-3.35a1.724 1.724 0 001.066-2.573c-.94-1.543.826-3.31 2.37-2.37.996.608 2.296.07 2.572-1.065z"></path>
									<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"></path>
								</svg>
							</div>
							<div>
								<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Geliştirici Deneyimi</h2>
								<p class="text-gray-300 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
									Minimalist olmak, geliştirici deneyiminden ödün vermek demek değil. 
									Tam tersine, daha iyi bir deneyim sunuyoruz:
								</p>
								<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
									<div class="bg-dark-tertiary rounded-lg p-4 border border-dark-border">
										<h3 class="text-white font-semibold mb-2">⚡ Anında Başlangıç</h3>
										<p class="text-sm text-gray-400">30ms'den daha hızlı uygulama başlangıcı</p>
									</div>
									<div class="bg-dark-tertiary rounded-lg p-4 border border-dark-border">
										<h3 class="text-white font-semibold mb-2">🔄 Hot Reload</h3>
										<p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Değişiklikler anında yansır</p>
									</div>
									<div class="bg-dark-tertiary rounded-lg p-4 border border-dark-border">
										<h3 class="text-white font-semibold mb-2">🛠️ Basit CLI</h3>
										<p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Karmaşık komutlar yok</p>
									</div>
									<div class="bg-dark-tertiary rounded-lg p-4 border border-dark-border">
										<h3 class="text-white font-semibold mb-2">📦 Tek Binary</h3>
										<p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Dağıtım hiç bu kadar kolay olmamıştı</p>
									</div>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<!-- CTA Section -->
				<div class="mt-16 text-center">
					<div class="glass p-8 rounded-xl max-w-2xl mx-auto">
						<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
							Hazır mısın?
						</h2>
						<p class="text-gray-300 mb-6">
							Masaüstü uygulama geliştirmeyi en minimal ve en güçlü haliyle deneyimle.
						</p>
						<div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center space-y-4 sm:space-y-0 sm:space-x-4">
							<a href="/docs" class="btn-primary w-full sm:w-auto">
								Dokümantasyon
							</a>
							<a href="https://github.com/ionyx-framework/ionyx" class="btn-secondary w-full sm:w-auto">
								GitHub
							</a>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</BaseLayout>
